text: Eunidia simplex is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Charles Joseph Gahan in 1890.BioLib.cz - Eunidia simplex. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1890 Category:Taxa named by Charles Joseph Gahan
